import React from 'react'
import Header from '../../Conteudo/Header/Header'
import Footer from '../../Conteudo/Footer/Footer'
import Carousel from '../../Conteudo/Carousel/Carousel'

const PaginaInicial = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Header/>
            <Carousel/>
            <Footer/>
        </>
    )
}

export default PaginaInicial
